transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling VasoSite. This is John. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, John, just a couple of questions.

Speaker 1: I bought a... I ordered three bottles of your product.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I'm on my third bottle.

Speaker 1: Nothing's happened. I mean, there's nothing.

Speaker 2: There's no, you know, there's no results.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: So, I'm on... I've been taking it on an empty stomach like they told me to,

Speaker 1: but nothing seems to be happening.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Should I continue the third bottle or what?

Speaker 2: I mean, there are some people that it just takes longer.

Speaker 1: One thing I was going to say is I have had people tell me that they've switched to taking three.

Speaker 2: I realize that'll get through the bottle quicker, but when they switched to three,

Speaker 1: they did notice some better results, so that may be something worth considering, too.

Speaker 2: Okay, and then in the meantime, if I get through that third bottle,

Speaker 1: if nothing happens, I'm going to return the bottles to you on... for a full refund, right?

Speaker 2: I mean, it depends on when the order was ordered,

Speaker 1: but yeah, if it's within the 90-day window, yes, you can do that.

Speaker 2: Okay. Well, I'm just... I don't know. I'm just...

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: I'm just always wondering. Nothing seems to be going on.

Speaker 1: I got you. It... I mean, while we do have success with it,

Speaker 2: supplements are a little tricky. It's different for everybody, but like I said,

Speaker 1: I have heard people tell me taking three has kind of kicked things into gear for them,

Speaker 2: so that may be worth at least experimenting with.

Speaker 1: Okay. I'll check it out and call you back. What's your name?

Speaker 2: My name's John.

Speaker 1: All right, John. Thanks.

Speaker 2: Thanks. Bye-bye.
